  <brief_title>Effect of Probiotic Fermented Dairy Drinks on Intestinal Immune Response</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study on the Effects of Probiotic Fermented Dairy Drinks on the Intestinal Immune Response in Healthy Adults</official_title>
